Feature: Hotel Booking In The Adactin Application

Scenario: User Login In The Web Application
    Given user Launch The Adactin Application
    When  user Enter The User Name In User Field
    And   user Enter The Password In Password Field 
    Then  user Click The Login Button And Navigate TO Search Hotel Page 
    
    
Scenario: User Booking The Hotel 
    When  user Select The Location 
    And   user Select The Hotel 
    And   user Select  The  Room Type 
    And   user Select The Number Of Rooms 
    And   user Enter The Valid Check In Date 
    And   user Enter The valid Check Out Date 
    And   user Select Adult Per Room
    And   user Select The Childrens Per Room  
    Then  user Click The Search Button And Navigate To Select Hotel page 
    
Scenario: User Verify By Booking Details 
    When user Verify and click The Radio Button
    Then user Click The Continue Button And Navigate To Book A Hotel Page 
    
Scenario: Book Hotel To Hotel Functionality
    When  user Enter The First Name 
    And   user Enter The Last Name 
    And   user Enter The Billing Address
    And   user Enter The Valid Credit Card Number 
    And   user Select The Credit Card tye 
    And   user Select the Expire Month 
    And   user Select The Expire Year
    And   user Enter The Valid Cvv Number
    Then  user Click the Book Now Button And Navigate To
    
Scenario: scenario description
    Given a precondition is valid
    When an action is performed
    Then something should be asserted